title: Mad Men Season 1 Complete.rar
description:
I could not find the Complete Season 1 of Mad Men anywhere.  So over the last two weeks I managed to get all 13 episodes and have now combined them in one big file.

I apologize to all the original episode torrent creators, I did not record your info, and so cannot give full credit where it&#039;s due for your work.  Sorry.

I don&#039;t have any of the tech specs handy, however I know the following:

A/V sync is above average - there doesn&#039;t appear to be any lag.

Audio is average

Video is average - it looks pretty good on my computer, and definitely does not make full use of my Plasma TVs full capabilities.

Enjoy.
